## Description
The **Batch program&nbsp;**resource&nbsp;allows to process data in a batch workflow using a Java or Python program.

For more information, see:&nbsp;[How to Create a Java Program for a Batch Workflow](https://code.doxee.com/confluence/display/DS/How+to+Create+a+Java+Program+for+a+Batch+Workflow).

None.
